item.title: Selena Gomez Was Not Pregnant: Rep Calls Report 100 Percent Fictional
item.description: Calm down, Internet. Selena Gomez was not pregnant back in 2012, her rep confirms to Us Weekly. The rumor is "100 percent fictional," her rep tells Us. In Touch reported this week that Gomez, 21, got pregnant in 2012 — when she was still with Justin Bieber — but miscarried the baby. The magazine also alleged that she wanted to have the child and went into a "downward spiral" soon after that led to her rehab stay…two years later.

item.title: Sonya Deville Height, Weight, Age, Girlfriend, Family, Facts, Biography
item.description: Sonya Deville Quick Info Height 5 ft 7 in Weight 59 kg Date of Birth September 24, 1993 Zodiac Sign Libra Girlfriend Arianna Johnson Sonya Deville is an American professional wrestler known for her successful wrestling career. She is a member of the wrestling trio, Absolution and is represented by WWE Inc. She has a mild social media fan base with more than 400k followers on Instagram and more than 200k followers on Twitter.

item.title: Taylor Lautner Biography, Age, Wiki, Height, Weight, Girlfriend, Family & More
item.description: Taylor Lautner is an American actor, model, and martial artist probably most famous for portraying Jacob Black in the film series “The Twilight Saga.” Lautner was named one of Hollywood’s “50 Sexiest Men” after rising to notoriety as a teen star. He was also the highest-paid teen actor in the United States. Lautner is a martial arts fan who also enjoys football, baseball, jazz, and hip-hop dance. Lautner, a three-time ‘Junior World’ martial arts champion, made his way into Hollywood via sheer hard work and perseverance.

item.title: Willie Simmons Net Worth & Salary | How Much Does He Earn?
item.description: Willie Simmons, the former head coach of Florida A&M, amassed a substantial wealth while at Florida. It appears to be on the rise, however, with his recent transfer to Duke University. With a net worth in the millions, the college football coach is thriving in his profession and poised to earn a large salary in his new position. Willie Simmons was born in Florida, United States, on October 12, 1980.

item.title: Cardi B And Offset Celebrate Kulture's Birthday At Disneyland Paris
item.description: Cardi B and Offset took Kulture‘s birthday celebration overseas with a trip to Disneyland Paris. Documented by the “Bodak Yellow” rapper on social media, the family affair featured fun for the children as well as the adults during the day away. The outing included rides, special moments with characters, amusement park food, and more for Kulture, who officially celebrates the big day on Wednesday (July 10). Kulture is the on-again-off-again couple’s eldest child together.

item.title: Charleston White Net Worth 2023
item.description: Charleston White’s net worth is $1.5 million and he earns an annual salary of over $200,000 from his multiple income streams as an African-American entrepreneur, motivational speaker, YouTuber, founder and CEO of HYPE Youth Outreach, and social media personality. Charleston White gained fame after he turned back on his life of crime and ventured into content creation on YouTube. He eventually gained public attention following his comments about George Floyd and DMX.

item.title: Jude Walton: Homicide probe launched after ex-commissioner found dead 'with obvious signs of trauma'
item.description: ANN ARBOR, MICHIGAN: A 51-year-old former police oversight commissioner was found dead at her home in Ann Arbor on Thursday, April 13. Jude Walton, 51, served as the commissioner of the Independent Community Oversight Commissioner in Ann Arbor. Ann Arbor police who have launched a homicide probe said they arrived at the slain woman's residence in the 200 block of Chapin Street at around 1.30 pm to conduct a welfare check.

item.title: Kim Cattrall Mourns Death of Mom Shane at 93: 'Rest in Peace Mum'
item.description: Paying tribute. Kim Cattrall announced the death of her mom, Shane Cattrall, in a heartfelt post honoring her mother’s life. “Shane Cattrall 1929 – 2022,” the Sex and the City alum, 66, wrote via Instagram on Tuesday, December 20, alongside a carousel of photos of her and her mother throughout the years. “Rest in peace Mum ❤️.” Shane’s death comes seven months after the Crossroads actress honored her mom with a sweet photo and sentiment she shared on Mother’s Day.

The Fiend Tears Out Daniel Bryans Hair After Bringing Back The Yes Movement
item.description: Daniel Bryan closed out tonight’s episode of Friday Night SmackDown by bringing back a fan favorite. After being taunted by Bray Wyatt for a majority of the night, Bryan addressed the issue in the ring. Bryan said that both Wyatt and fans have been asking him to bring back the “Yes!” movement, and that since everyone wants him too, he will. From there, Bryan said that he would accept another challenge from the Fiend.

item.description: Getty/TMZ Bam Margera's son Phoenix is inspiring him to detox and sober up following a psych hold ... and his estranged wife is allowing him to talk to their kid again. Nikki Margera's attorney, David Glass, tells TMZ ... she's given the green light for Bam and Phoenix to start communicating, and they're talking over FaceTime while Bam's in rehab. We're told Bam's FaceTime sessions with Phoenix are being modulated by one of Bam's therapists .
